Congratulations for producing a magnificent website on the Vietnam War. I teach history to students aged 11-18 in England. I have produced a website guide for students studying the Vietnam War.<br><br>
http://www3.mistral.co.uk/spartacus/vietintro.htm<br><br>
As you will see I have encouraged the students to visit your website. My site includes an 'Investigations' section. Would you like to contribute some possible project ideas? This will enable you to influence the issues that young people look at when studying the Vietnam War. <br><br>
Feel free to add a link to our website if you like what we have done.<br><br>
